<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Erro interno - Sistema de Almoxarifado</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/neumorphic.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div style="min-height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; background: var(--bg-primary);">
        <div class="neu-card" style="text-align: center; max-width: 600px;">
            <div style="font-size: 6rem; margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);">⚠️</div>
            <h1 style="font-size: var(--font-size-3xl); font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: var(--space-md);">
                Erro interno do servidor
            </h1>
            <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: var(--space-xl); line-height: 1.6;">
                Ocorreu um erro inesperado. Nossa equipe foi notificada e está trabalhando para resolver o problema.
            </p>
            
            <% if (error && process.env.NODE_ENV === 'development') { %>
                <div class="neu-alert neu-alert-danger" style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);">
                    <h3 style="margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);">Detalhes do erro (desenvolvimento):</h3>
                    <pre style="font-size: var(--font-size-xs); overflow-x: auto; white-space: pre-wrap;">
<%= error.stack %>
                    </pre>
                </div>
            <% } %>
            
            <div style="display: flex; gap: var(--space-md); justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;">
                <a href="/dashboard" class="neu-btn neu-btn-primary">
                    🏠 Ir para o Dashboard
                </a>
                <button onclick="location.reload()" class="neu-btn">
                    🔄 Tentar novamente
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>